# CODEOWNERS — omiiCARE_QA
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# This file declares who is automatically requested for review when matching
# paths change. GitHub reads it (root, .github/, or docs/ location) and assigns
# the listed owners as required reviewers on pull requests.
#
# Syntax: <path-pattern>  <owner> [<owner> ...]
# - Later, more specific matches override earlier, broader ones.
# - Owners are GitHub usernames/teams prefixed with '@'.
#
# omiiCARE_QA is currently a SINGLE-MAINTAINER repository, so every path is owned
# by @omiinayak25. The per-module lines below are intentional: they mark the
# seams where dedicated team handles (e.g. @omiinayak25/backend-team) will take
# over ownership as the project grows. Until then, all roads lead to the
# maintainer. See CONTRIBUTING.md for the review process.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

